OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe court has already heard that when
OL,8,Fhemmed in by police cars, Mr Kaba,
OL,9,Ftried to ram his way past, between a
OL,10,Fmarked police car and a Tesla parked
OL,11,Fnearby. Mr Blake is accused of murder,
OL,12,Fwhich he denies.
OL,14,FHe told the jury that he felt "awful"
OL,15,Ffollowing the shooting and has
OL,16,Freplayed events in his head since.
