OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAsked what he was thinking immediately
OL,8,Fafter the shooting, he said: "First of
OL,9,Fall I was relieved that the car noise
OL,10,Fsubsided, relieved my colleagues were
OL,11,FOK.
OL,13,F"Then I just felt awful."
OL,15,FHe told the court that since the
OL,16,Fshooting he thinks about what happened
OL,17,F"every day, all the time" and replays
OL,18,Fit in his head a lot.
