OL,7,FMembers of Mr Kaba's family sat in
OL,8,Fcourt listening to Mr Blake give
OL,9,Fevidence.
OL,11,FHe told the court that prior to the
OL,12,Fshooting he'd never fired a gun at a
OL,13,Freal human being or seen a colleague
OL,14,Ffire a gun at a real human being.
