OL,4,Ccolleague was 'about to die', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe added he did not intend to kill, as
OL,8,Fthe training he received is to fire to
OL,9,Fincapacitate. He said he fired because
OL,10,Fhe wanted Chris Kaba's vehicle to
OL,11,Fstop, and that he wasn't angry,
OL,12,Ffrustrated or annoyed before during or
OL,13,Fafter he fired shots.
OL,15,FWorking in firearms means that you
OL,16,Fface "the most dangerous and
OL,17,Fpotentially the most violent" people
OL,18,Fin London, the officer told the court,
OL,19,Fadding: "It's daunting but it's a very
OL,20,Frewarding job."
