OL,7,F"I thought I was the only person with
OL,8,Feffective firearms cover at the time.
OL,9,FIf I hadn't acted I thought one of my
OL,10,Fcolleagues would be dead. I felt I had
OL,11,Fa duty to protect them at the time."
OL,13,FThe trial continues.
